==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Instroke
<hw>In"stroke`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An inward stroke;
specif., in a steam or other engine, a stroke in which the piston is
moving away from the crank shaft; -- opposed to
<contr>outstroke</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Instruct</ent>⟦br⟧
